            "title": "盤中速報 - 羅威(LOW-US)大漲5.06%，報230.69美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>羅威(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:LOW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/LOW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">LOW-US</a>)截至台北時間19日23:39股價上漲11.12美元，報230.69美元，漲幅5.06%，成交量3,003,487（股），盤中最高價230.69美元、最低價224.26美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.1%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.81%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+1.42%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+2.7%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>羅威(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:LOW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/LOW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">LOW-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-4.39%</li> <li>近 1 月：-8.05%</li> <li>近 3 月：-10.32%</li> <li>近 6 月：-4.02%</li> <li>今年以來：-8.9%</li></ul></section></main>",
